snippet.textDisplay: Absolutely beautiful. The first song was so pleasant and nice. I saw a lot of comments saying that we are united by culture, which is so true, We are after all part of the same syncretic culture. Laung Gawacha would be heard as much in a Punjabi wedding in Delhi or Amritsar as it would be in a Muslim wedding in Lahore or Multan. This cultural affinity can't be described in words. Speechless!
snippet.textOriginal: Absolutely beautiful. The first song was so pleasant and nice.
